Hands down the best Subway in the area. Whenever we crave a footlong, we make sure to go the extra distance to have one from here even thought there are closer options available. The owners are very considerate and they always change their gloves and wash their knives before making our sandwiches as we’re vegetarians. They always seem to put in the right proportions of sauces and veggies which makes for a perfect sub almost every time. Try this location if you’re around and you won’t be disappointed!
